    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nCurrently, progress messages are displayed as just text. However, progress messages provide more information in the title, percent, and status fields. Also, messages with the same ID don't get replaced in UI with `vim._core.ui2`. It should support progress messages properly.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nSupport title, status, and percent fields for progress messages.",
